0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(OVERVIEW) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(This guide covers the fictional SCN-512 warehouse scanner when completed picks, moves, or) Tj
0 -14 Td
(counts do not sync promptly to the host system. It focuses on the difference between local) Tj
0 -14 Td
(device issues, wireless coverage problems, and backlog on the application side.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(COMMON SYMPTOMS) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Scanner shows completed work locally but the supervisor dashboard still displays the old) Tj
0 -14 Td
(queue state after several minutes.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Users see a sync-pending banner that clears and returns repeatedly without a hard error) Tj
0 -14 Td
(message.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Scanner reconnects to Wi-Fi after roaming but does not upload queued work until the app is) Tj
0 -14 Td
(restarted.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Multiple devices in one aisle report stale inventory positions after a wireless access point) Tj
0 -14 Td
(switchover.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(LIKELY CAUSES) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Weak or unstable wireless coverage causing repeated partial reconnects.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Clock drift or stale authentication token after the device resumes from a long dock period.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Application queue backlog on the local device caused by a stuck job record.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Server-side processing delay affecting multiple scanners at once.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(DIAGNOSTIC WORKFLOW) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Check whether the problem is isolated to one scanner, one aisle, or an entire shift crew) Tj
0 -14 Td
(before making device-level changes.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Confirm Wi-Fi signal and roaming history on the device diagnostics page. Note whether) Tj
0 -14 Td
(reconnects occurred during the affected window.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Open the sync queue screen and look for one item that remains in retry longer than the) Tj
0 -14 Td
(others.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Verify device time, battery state, and token age if the unit has been docked for an extended) Tj
0 -14 Td
(period.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- If multiple devices are affected, compare the observed time with any known network or) Tj
0 -14 Td
(application maintenance notice before clearing queues.) Tj
ET
